author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Today I'm looking at the pressure on musicians to create content for social media and in particular, for TikTok. It's a pact that can pay off - with exposure to a wider audience, but it can also backfire. It's done both for.a band called Panic Shack - but it's not been easy. 

To see more from Panic Shack, visit their page: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMV_H2YjdXmzp5DLRywnIYQ

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

title: Musicians on TikTok: A Necessary Pact?
